      "instruction": "<p>Heat a pot with a matching lid with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>black mustard seeds</strong> and cook for 30 secs, stirring continuously, until fragrant</p><p>Rinse the <strong>white long grain rice</strong> until the water runs clear, then add it to the pot with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and stir to fully coat the grains</p>",
